name: sbiifsccodesapi
short_description:
This project is an initiative to provide great features with the help of API access.

The API access is public and it is free to use without any limitations. Users can use it for personal and commercial purposes. The admin of Statebankofindiaifsccode.com done a great job for this project. The hosted project was very good with accurate data and it's complete and very easy to use.

This will offer info fields like ifsc codes, micr code, branch code, address, customer care, etc. You can also refer this www.statebankofindiaifsccode.in

Here are some sample output data:

SBI New Colony
The State Bank of India New Colony branch ifsc code is SBIN0000645 for online NEFT transactions and micr code is 110002200 for cheque processing. New Colony was located in gurgaon, haryana and branch address is New Colony, Gurgaon, Haryana, Pin 122001 for SBI IFSC SBIN0000645.

SBI Firozpur Jhirka
The State Bank of India Firozpur Jhirka branch ifsc code is SBIN0001071 for online NEFT.
summary: Access SBI IFSC Codes and MICR Codes via API
